<!DOCTYPE html>
<html :class="{ 'theme-dark': dark }" x-data="data()" lang="en">
<%- include('head') %>

    <body>
        <div class="flex h-screen bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900" :class="{ 'overflow-hidden': isSideMenuOpen}">
            <%- include('aside') %>
                <div class="flex flex-col flex-1">
                    <%- include('header') %>
                        <main class="pb-16 pr-10 overflow-y-auto max-w-5xl mx-auto">
                            <h1 class="text-6xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Privacy Policy</h1>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Thank you for considering our mailing service. At our company, we are committed to
                                protecting your privacy and maintaining the confidentiality of your personal
                                information. This privacy policy describes how we collect, use, and share your personal
                                data in connection with our mailing service.</p>
                            <h2 class="my-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">1. Information We Collect</h2>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">We collect the following types of personal information from our users:</p>
                            <ul class="flex flex-col items-start flex-shrink-0">
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Contact Information: We collect your name, email address, and any other contact
                                    information you provide when you sign up for our mailing service.</li>
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Usage Information: We collect information about how you use our mailing service,
                                    including the frequency and duration of your use, the types of emails you send and
                                    receive, and any other interactions with our service.</li>
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Technical Information: We collect technical information about your device and
                                    internet connection, such as your IP address, browser type, operating system, and
                                    other similar data.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2 class="my-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">We use your personal information for the following purposes:</p>
                            <ul class="flex flex-col items-start flex-shrink-0">
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Providing Our Service: We use your information to provide you with our mailing
                                    service and to respond to any requests or inquiries you may have.</li>
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Improving Our Service: We use your information to analyze how our service is used
                                    and to improve its functionality, features, and performance.</li>
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Marketing and Advertising: We may use your information to send you marketing and
                                    promotional communications about our service, including newsletters, updates, and
                                    other information that we believe may be of interest to you.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2 class="my-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">3. How We Share Your Information</h2>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">We do not share your personal information with any third parties except in the following
                                circumstances:</p>
                            <ul class="flex flex-col items-start flex-shrink-0">
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers
                                    who perform services on our behalf, such as email delivery and data analysis.</li>
                                <li class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 list-inside list-disc">Legal Requirements: We may share your information when required to do so by law or
                                    to comply with legal process.</li>
                            </ul>
                            <h2 class="my-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">4. How We Protect Your Information</h2>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">We use reasonable and appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your
                                personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, and use. We regularly review
                                and update our security procedures to ensure that your information is protected against
                                the latest threats.</p>
                            <h2 class="my-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">5. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">You have certain rights and choices regarding your personal information, including the
                                right to access, correct, or delete your information, as well as the right to object to
                                certain uses of your information. You may also opt-out of receiving marketing and
                                promotional communications from us at any time.</p>
                            <h2 class="my-6 text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">We may update this privacy policy from time to time to reflect changes in our business or
                                to comply with legal requirements. If we make any material changes to this policy, we
                                will provide notice to our users in accordance with applicable law.</p>
                            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy or our handling of your
                                personal information, please contact us using the contact information provided on our
                                website.</p>
                        </main>
                </div>
        </div>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/alpinejs/alpine@v2.x.x/dist/alpine.min.js"></script>
    </body>

</html>